    <div class="controls">
        <h2>합격랩 개인시간표 설정</h2>
        <div class="input-group">
            <div class="input-item">
                <label>이름:</label>
                <input type="text" id="inputName" placeholder="이름 입력" oninput="updateInfo()">
            </div>
            <div class="input-item">
                <label>이용기간:</label>
                <input type="text" id="inputPeriod" placeholder="예: ~12/31" oninput="updateInfo()">
            </div>
            <div class="input-item">
                <label>좌석 번호:</label>
                <input type="text" id="inputSeat" placeholder="S-7" oninput="updateInfo()">
            </div>
            <div class="input-item">
                <label>사물함 번호:</label>
                <input type="text" id="inputLocker" placeholder="번호 입력" oninput="updateInfo()">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="btn-group">
            <button class="btn-reset" onclick="resetTable()">전체 초기화</button>
            <button class="btn-all-x" onclick="setAllNoEntry()">전체 입실안함</button>
            <button class="btn-download" onclick="downloadImage()">이미지 저장</button>
            <button class="btn-print" onclick="window.print()">인쇄하기</button>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">* 시간표 칸을 클릭하여 상태를 변경하세요. (빈칸 → 학습(○) → 입실안함 → 빈칸)</p>
    </div>

    <div id="preview-area">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="title">합격랩 개인시간표</div>
            <table class="info-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="info-label">이름</td>
                    <td id="displayName">이름 입력</td>
                    <td class="info-label">이용기간</td>
                    <td id="displayPeriod">예: ~12/31</td>
                    <td class="info-label">좌석 번호</td>
                    <td id="displaySeat">S-7</td>
